name: Cell Wars (itch)
description:
You are the cells on the top left. Your dream is world domination, but the other cells have the same idea!

Draw energy from your energy cells to expand and kill the other cells!

Cells:

Skull - Use energy to destroy adjacent enemy cells

Energy - Produce & transfer energy to adjacent cells. 

Chemistry - Use energy to reproduce to adjacent cell

Gameplay:

Press your cells to change it's type!
